&lt;h4&gt;


  CloudFormation
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-stack references: export values from one stack (Outputs/Export) and import them in another stack (ImportValue). Export names must be unique within the same account and region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Change set is used when you change the template. Depending on the changes made, either in-place update or replacement are performed. (â€»In case of replacement, the resource is recreated. Some parameters like EC2 instance ID are changed.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

